<div class="block">
	<h5>
		FAQ's
	</h5>
	<div class="content">
		<dl class="faq">
			<dt>
				How does Tawala work?
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<ul style="margin-top:0px;">
					<li>
						Look for a module you want to use in Tawala's library.
					</li>
					<li>
						Download it from the library and personalize it.
					</li>
					<li>
						Deploy it and use its URL as a link on your Website or email
					</li>
				</ul>
			</dd>


			<dt>
				How is Tawala different from a typical forms creation program?
			</dt>
			<dd>
				Tawala is all about what you can do with the information you have gathered with online forms. 
				Its processes can calculate intermediate data, compare records, compile statistics, and 
				assemble documents and web pages based on your clients' responses.
			</dd>

			<dt>
				What if I can't find what I need in your community library?
			</dt>

			<dd>
				Create your own project with Tawala Designer, our authoring tool. Or put your project 
				idea up in the Discussions forum and see if someone else can build it for you.
			</dd>

		</dl>
		<a href="/faq">More...</a>
	</div>
</div>
